123
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:38,080
Ruoyao, how could you...

124
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,800
I can't stand by

125
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,240
when you are in danger for me.

126
00:08:42,160 --> 00:08:43,040
We might talk about it

127
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:46,400
