138
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,360
Don't get Cangwu involved.

139
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:45,320
Shunqin.

140
00:09:46,460 --> 00:09:46,960
Look.

141
00:09:48,860 --> 00:09:52,700
